<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>出版物 |皮尤研究中心</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/publications/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:07:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>与许多其他国家的人相比，美国人不太可能认为赌博在道德上是错误的</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/16/americans-are-less-likely-than-people-in-many-other-countries-to-see-gambling-as-morally-wrong/</link><description>在许多其他接受调查的国家，大约一半或更多的成年人认为赌博是不道德的。其中印度尼西亚为 89%，印度为 83%，意大利为 71%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/16/americans-are-less-likely-than-people-in-many-other-countries-to-see-gambling-as-morally-wrong/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普上任第一年联邦劳动力减少10%</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/13/federal-workforce-shrank-10-in-trumps-first-year-back-in-office/</link><description>2025 年，联邦劳动力将减少 10.3%，失去近 238,000 名工人。在主要机构中，教育部和美国国际开发署的削减幅度最大。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 01:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/13/federal-workforce-shrank-10-in-trumps-first-year-back-in-office/</guid></item><item><title>大多数美国人仍然认为堕胎在所有或大多数情况下都应该合法</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/2026/03/12/majority-of-americans-continue-to-say-abortion-should-be-legal-in-all-or-most-cases/</link><description>60% 的大多数美国成年人表示，在所有或大多数情况下堕胎都应该合法。这一比例较过去几年略有下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 01:05:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/2026/03/12/majority-of-americans-continue-to-say-abortion-should-be-legal-in-all-or-most-cases/</guid></item><item><title>公众对堕胎的看法</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/fact-sheet/public-opinion-on-abortion/</link><description>堕胎在美国长期以来一直是一个有争议的问题，也是美国人在党派、意识形态和宗教方面产生严重分歧的一个问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Jun 2025 00:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/fact-sheet/public-opinion-on-abortion/</guid></item><item><title>关于美国人如何看待人工智能的主要发现</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/12/key-findings-about-how-americans-view-artificial-intelligence/</link><description>根据皮尤研究中心五年来的调查，以下是关于美国人如何使用和看待人工智能，以及他们在哪里看到前景和风险的 13 项调查结果。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:50:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/12/key-findings-about-how-americans-view-artificial-intelligence/</guid></item><item><title>美国人如何看待数据中心对从环境​​到就业等关键领域的影响</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/12/how-americans-view-data-centers-impact-in-key-areas-from-the-environment-to-jobs/</link><description>更多的美国人表示数据中心对环境、家庭能源成本和附近人们的生活质量产生负面影响，而不是产生积极影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:35:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/12/how-americans-view-data-centers-impact-in-key-areas-from-the-environment-to-jobs/</guid></item><item><title>为何佛教在全球范围内日渐式微？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/11/why-is-buddhism-shrinking-worldwide/</link><description>2010 年至 2020 年间，全球佛教徒人口减少了约 5%，是唯一出现下降的主要宗教团体。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 00:59:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/11/why-is-buddhism-shrinking-worldwide/</guid></item><item><title>关于美国佛教徒的 5 个事实</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/11/5-facts-about-buddhists-in-the-united-states/</link><description>今天，美国有数百万佛教徒，其中包括许多出生于佛教家庭的人和其他皈依该宗教的人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 00:44:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/11/5-facts-about-buddhists-in-the-united-states/</guid></item><item><title>佛教最近在东亚的衰落</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/2026/03/11/buddhisms-recent-decline-in-east-asia/</link><description>佛教是唯一一个在 2010 年至 2020 年间全球人口减少的主要宗教。了解佛教在东亚（尤其是日本和韩国）人口减少的原因。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 00:29:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/2026/03/11/buddhisms-recent-decline-in-east-asia/</guid></item><item><title>随着奥斯卡颁奖典礼的临近，看看美国人的观影习惯</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/06/as-the-academy-awards-approach-a-look-at-moviegoing-habits-in-the-united-states/</link><description>大约一半的美国人 (53%) 在 2025 年夏季的一项调查中表示，他们去年在电影院看过一部电影。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 01:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/03/06/as-the-academy-awards-approach-a-look-at-moviegoing-habits-in-the-united-states/</guid></item></channel></rss>